  <h1 class="text-2xl mb-4">[05] Large scale update in Q1 2018</h1>

  <p>[ 2017.12.28 ]</p>

  <p>Hi. Ragnarok users. Ragnarok Zero team of RO1 studio. Today, we are announcing a massive update in the first quarter of 2018, which is being prepared by our Ragnarok Zero team.</p>

  <h2>Update schedule</h2>

  <p>Many teams related to Ragnarok Zero are currently working hard to stabilize the service. Our first goal is to provide you with a stable service and we will be ready to update soon. The large-scale update is scheduled for January 31st.</p>

  <h2>2nd class skill updates</h2>

  <p>Some of the second class skills will be revised. The contents are as follows.</p>

  <h3>2-1 Classes</h3>

  <h4>Knight</h4>

  <ul class="list-disc pl-8">
    <li><b>Two-handed quicken</b>: Increases ASPD (10% reduced after attack delay).</li>
  </ul>

  <h4>Blacksmith</h4>

  <ul class="list-disc pl-8">
    <li><b>Adrenaline Rush</b>: Increases ASPD (10% reduced after attack delay).</li>
    <li><b>Power Thrust</b>: No longer destroys weapon. Increases ATK at a higher rate for party members.</li>
    <li><b>Weapon Production</b>: Gives random options to the level 3 weapon being produced. Number of random options based on ranking (up to 5 options).</li>
  </ul>

  <h4>Wizard</h4>

  <ul class="list-disc pl-8">
    <li><b>Meteor Storm</b>: Cast modification (fixed cast rate modification).</li>
    <li><b>Storm Gust</b>: Decreased cast time, increased skill cooldown.</li>
    <li><b>Lord of Vermimlion</b>: Decreased cast time.</li>
  </ul>

  <h4>Priest</h4>

  <ul class="list-disc pl-8">
    <li><b>Suffragium</b>: Removed count limit, buff full party within range.</li>
    <li><b>Impositio Manus</b>: Increases equipment ATK, MATK, and buffs full party within range.</li>
    <li><b>Magnus Exorcimus</b>: Decreased cast time.</li>
  </ul>

  <h4>Hunter</h4>

  <ul class="list-disc pl-8">
    <li><b>Blitz Beat</b>: Removed damage dispersion effect of auto Blitz Beat.</li>
    <li><b>Landmine</b>: Fixed cast.</li>
    <li><b>Blast Mine</b>: Fixed cast.</li>
    <li><b>Claymore Trap</b>: Modified casting.</li>
  </ul>

