  <h4>Crusader</h4>

  <ul class="list-disc pl-8">
    <li><b>Spear Quicken</b>: Increases ASPD (10% reduced after attack delay).</li>
    <li><b>Grand Cross</b>: Removed feedback damage (keep 20% HP reduction penalty), fixed casting.</li>
  </ul>

  <h4>Alchemist</h4>

  <ul class="list-disc pl-8">
