    <li><b>Acid Terror</b>: Increased armor destruction probability.</li>
  </ul>

  <h4>Sage</h4>

  <ul class="list-disc pl-8">
    <li><b>Earth Spike</b>: Increases damage.</li>
    <li><b>Heaven's Drive</b>: Decreased casting.</li>
  </ul>

  <h4>Monk</h4>

  <ul class="list-disc pl-8">
    <li><b>Change knuckle size penalty</b>: Small 100% / Medium 100% / Large 75%</li>
  </ul>

